<Layout title="Javier Fuertes | About Me">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-24 sm:pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-10 sm:pb-16 md:pb-24">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 sm:gap-10 md:gap-12 items-center md:items-start">
      <!-- Author photo -->
      <div class="shrink-0">
        <div class="w-40 h-40 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 md:w-56 md:h-56 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-zinc-800 ring-1 ring-zinc-700">
          <img
            src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E03AQF7d2Fy-jZzQw/profile-displayphoto-crop_800_800/B4EZu8XqiHI4AM-/0/1768391881957?e=1771459200&v=beta&t=7bHFrS81p1Hj4PC4WiVEFBtW1rds89fQkYBSeUw8Ox4"
            alt="Author portrait"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="space-y-5 sm:space-y-6 text-center md:text-left">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Javier Fuertes</h1>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-1 text-base sm:text-lg">Street & Landscape Photographer</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            My name is Javier Fuertes, a photographer from Spain with a passion for exploring the world one frame at a time. I’ve always been drawn to the beauty and rhythm of urban life as well as the quiet majesty of nature. Whether wandering through the streets of a new city or hiking into the wild, I aim to capture authentic moments that tell a story and reveal the atmosphere of each place I visit.
          </p>
          <p>
            My go‑to gear includes a Sony a6400 paired with a 16–50mm kit lens and a 28–70mm lens, giving me the versatility to shoot everything from sweeping landscapes to the fine details of city life. Through my photography, I hope to share the sense of wonder I feel when discovering new perspectives—inviting others to see the world through my lens.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not behind the lens, I enjoy learning new languages, watching series or playing the ukulele.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact / social links -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-3 sm:gap-4 pt-2">
